            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                P<supplied reason="lost">ro s</supplied>alute <expan><abbr>collegi</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>iuventutis et <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> Marce<lb break="no" n="3"/>llini et <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> M&amp;lt;a&amp;gt;rcelli <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectorum</ex></expan> et Maximi et Ursi <lb n="5"/>patres <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Gell</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Marcelli<lb break="no" n="6"/>nus et <abbr>Pant</abbr> Tertius <lb n="7"/>et <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Valerius <expan><abbr>qq</abbr><ex>uaestores</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>coll</abbr><ex>egii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>cripti</ex></expan> ex voto <lb n="9"/>posuerunt </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex cert="low"/></expan><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex cert="low"/>no</expan> <abbr>Marcell</abbr> Valeriu<supplied reason="lost">s <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftfeld von zwei Nischen flankiert; in der linken eine, in der rechten zwei männliche Figuren, wohl Angehörige des collegium iuventutis. Z. 10 steht auf dem unteren Rahmen. (B): AIJ: Z. 3: Marcelli; ILS: Z. 6: P. Ant. Tertius; CIL 03, 04045; Weber; Hudeczek: Z. 10: [---]ino.</p>
